OL,3,C'Trick or treat' shouted before Armagh
OL,4,Cbar arson attack, court told
OL,6,FA man facing attempted murder charges
OL,7,Fafter an arson attack on a busy bar in
OL,8,FArmagh allegedly shouted "trick or
OL,9,Ftreat" before throwing a lit petrol
OL,10,Fbomb directly at two people inside, a
OL,11,Fcourt has heard.
OL,13,FJohn Patrick Nixon, 38, appeared
OL,14,Fbefore a district judge in Newry, Co
OL,15,FDown on Wednesday accused of two
OL,16,Fcounts of attempted murder in relation
OL,17,Fto the incident in Armagh city on
OL,18,FMonday evening.
