OL,3,C'Trick or treat' shouted before Armagh
OL,4,Cbar arson attack, court told
OL,6,FNixon, who spoke briefly to confirm
OL,7,Fhis name, date of birth and that he
OL,8,Funderstood the charges, is also
OL,9,Fcharged with several other offences
OL,10,Falleged to have been committed on the
OL,11,Fsame day, including criminal damage to
OL,12,Fproperty and a vehicle elsewhere in
OL,13,FArmagh earlier that evening.
OL,15,FNo defence application for bail was
OL,16,Fmade at the remand hearing in Newry
OL,17,FMagistrates' Court on Wednesday and
OL,18,FNixon, who is from Irish Street in
OL,19,FArmagh, was remanded into custody to
OL,20,Fappear before a judge again next month.
