OL,3,C'Trick or treat' shouted before Armagh
OL,4,Cbar arson attack, court told
OL,6,FDuring the hearing, a detective
OL,7,Fconstable told the court that the Toby
OL,8,FJug bar on Irish Street had a
OL,9,Fsignificant number of people inside,
OL,10,Fincluding children, when the attack
OL,11,Funfolded shortly before 9pm.
OL,13,FCustomers were watching a football
OL,14,Fmatch on TV and traditional music was
OL,15,Falso being played when the incident
OL,16,Foccurred, the court heard.
