OL,3,C'Trick or treat' shouted before Armagh
OL,4,Cbar arson attack, court told
OL,6,F"Police attended and spoke with
OL,7,Fvictims and witnesses who stated that
OL,8,Fa male entered the pub, shouted 'trick
OL,9,For treat' and then threw a lit petrol
OL,10,Fbomb directly towards two people in
OL,11,Fthe bar," the officer said.
OL,13,FTwo men, one aged in his 30s and one
OL,14,Fin his 60s, were taken to hospital
OL,15,Fwith burn injuries described in court
OL,16,Fas "significant".
