OL,3,C'Trick or treat' shouted before Armagh
OL,4,Cbar arson attack, court told
OL,6,FThe detective constable told the court
OL,7,Fthat CCTV from outside the bar showed
OL,8,Fa man taking something from a plastic
OL,9,Fbag, walking across the road, then
OL,10,Flighting a rag protruding from a
OL,11,Fbottle.
OL,13,FHe said the CCTV showed a flash and
OL,14,Forange flames and glow of fire coming
OL,15,Fthrough the doorway of the pub shortly
OL,16,Fafter the man walked inside.
OL,18,F"The male suspect walks calmly out of
OL,19,Fthe bar, walks across the street
OL,20,Fwhilst removing an item from the
OL,21,Fwaistband of his trousers," he added.
