OL,6,F"As a number of children and an adult
OL,7,Fcame running out of the bar, he
OL,8,Fbrandishes this item, which appears to
OL,9,Fbe a large knife."
OL,11,FDistrict judge Eamonn King was told
OL,12,Fthat Nixon was arrested later that
OL,13,Fevening at an address on Chapel Lane
OL,14,Fin Armagh. The court heard that a
OL,15,Fpetrol bomb and a plastic bag
OL,16,Fcontaining a knife were located at the
OL,17,Fsame property.
