OL,3,C'Trick or treat' shouted before Armagh
OL,4,Cbar arson attack, court told
OL,6,FThe detective constable said officers
OL,7,Fhad also obtained CCTV footage from a
OL,8,Flocal filling station at around 7.50pm
OL,9,Fthat evening that allegedly shows the
OL,10,Faccused filling up a plastic bottle
OL,11,Fwith #2.03 worth of petrol.
OL,13,FAs well as two counts of attempted
OL,14,Fmurder, Nixon is also charged with
OL,15,Farson with intent to endanger life;
OL,16,Fpossession of a knife in a public
OL,17,Fplace; and three counts of criminal
OL,18,Fdamage.
