OL,3,C'Trick or treat' shouted before Armagh
OL,4,Cbar arson attack, court told
OL,6,FThe criminal damage charges relate to
OL,7,Fincidents on the Keady Road in Armagh
OL,8,Fin the early evening of Monday.
OL,10,FAt around 5.30pm, police received a
OL,11,Freport that a brick had been thrown
OL,12,Fthrough the window of a home on the
OL,13,Froad and the window of a car had been
OL,14,Fsmashed at the same property.
OL,16,FA short time later, another 999 call
OL,17,Fwas made reporting that a brick had
OL,18,Fbeen thrown through the kitchen window
OL,19,Fof another property nearby.
