OL,3,C'Trick or treat' shouted before Armagh
OL,4,Cbar arson attack, court told
OL,6,FCCTV from the area showed a bald man
OL,7,Fwearing dark clothing walking up the
OL,8,Fdrive of one of the properties at the
OL,9,Ftime.
OL,11,FThe detective constable told the court
OL,12,Fthat a local resident had identified
OL,13,Fthe male in the CCTV as Nixon.
OL,15,FThe officer said detectives had
OL,16,Festablished that the description of
OL,17,Fthe male who had caused the damage to
OL,18,Fthe windows matched that of the male
OL,19,Fwho had thrown the petrol bomb.
